Package: mobster
Type: Package
Title: MOBSTER - Model-based tumour subclonal deconvolution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Giulio Caravagna
Maintainer: Giulio Caravagna <gcaravagn@gmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Giulio", "Caravagna", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "gcaravagn@gmail.com")
Description: This package implmenets a finite Dirichlet mixture model with k Beta and 1 Pareto component; Beta components should map to actual alleles under positive selection, and the Pareto tail models alleles resulting from neutral evolutionary dynamics.
The package provides also the implementation of a variational inference method to fit semi-parametric Dirichlet mixture model with Binomial components, and a set of functions that help processing cancer genome sequencing data.
License: GPL
